				<td colspan="2"><span>Cha helps with charm/mez .
<br />

<br />
Thats a fact.
<br />

<br />
My method is simple..
<br />

<br />
Charm WILL break/resist.
<br />
Mez WILL get resists.
<br />

<br />
If i survive charm/mez being resists/broken, then I will have the mob recharmed/remezzed quickly.
<br />

<br />
So I dont worry about it breaking a bit more often, I worry about surviveing the breaks.
<br />

<br />
so, 
<br />

<br />
AC/HP &gt; Cha.
<br />

<br />

<br />

